A Drive-by shareing widget (share any web page in your tt-rss)
=================================================================

(This is a very preliminary installation instruction)

Make sure you have a dedicated gritttt feed in tt-rss.

Put files in a dir on your webserver.

Adjust path to form.html in dialog.js

Adjust path to your site in bookmarklet.js.
Copy content of bookmarklet.js in a bookmark of your browser.

(Later)

Adjust tt-rss credentials in the PHP file
